ForkTex Python is the unified command-line interface and agent runtime for
the ForkTex self-managed software factory. It bundles the local developer
agent, FSD (ForkTex Standard for Delivery) compliance tooling, architecture
discovery and audit, the menu-driven root loop, and orchestration glue
across the cloud, intelligence, and network services.

